OL,3,CInvestigation launched after body of
OL,4,Cteenage girl found in Kingsbury Water
OL,5,CPark
OL,7,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,8,Fafter the body of a teenage girl has
OL,9,Fbeen recovered from a waterpark in
OL,10,FWarwickshire.
OL,12,FPolice were called to Kingsbury Water
OL,13,FPark, on Bodymoor Heath Lane, just
OL,14,Fsouth of Tamworth shortly after 6pm
OL,15,Fyesterday evening (May 25).
OL,17,FA specialist search team, a police
OL,18,Fhelicopter, as well as the fire
OL,19,Fservice and ambulance carried out a
OL,20,Fsearch and the girl's body was then
OL,21,Ffound at 7:20pm.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
