PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779819070
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after body of
OL,4,Cteenage girl found in Kingsbury Water
OL,5,CPark
OL,7,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,8,Fservices, she was pronounced dead at
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,FA spokesman for Atherstone and
OL,12,FColeshill Police said: "We can confirm
OL,13,Fthat, sadly, the body of a teenage
OL,14,Fgirl was recovered from the water
OL,15,Fshortly after 7.20pm. Despite the
OL,16,Fefforts of emergency services, she was
OL,17,Fpronounced deceased at the scene.
OL,26,@tD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
