PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779819070
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after body of
OL,4,Cteenage girl found in Kingsbury Water
OL,5,CPark
OL,7,F"Her next of kin has been informed,
OL,8,Fand they are being supported by
OL,9,Fspecially trained officers. Over the
OL,10,Fcoming days, we will have officers in
OL,11,Fthe area providing reassurance, so if
OL,12,Fyou have any questions, please speak
OL,13,Fto them.
OL,15,F"An investigation into the
OL,16,Fcircumstances has begun, and we would
OL,17,Fask people to avoid speculation about
OL,18,Fwhat has happened. Our thoughts remain
OL,19,Fwith her family and friends during
OL,20,Fthis difficult time."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@UO]
